# Fedora 14

Step 1: Partition Disk

Name          Size          Partion
sda1          250MB         /Boot
sda2        10240MB         /
sda3         4000MB         SWEP
sda4        61323MB         /home


Step 2: Create User

Billlee:510:510

Step 3: Restoring authority and selinux Configuration
sudo chgrp -R billlee billlee
sudo chown -R billlee billlee
sudo restorecon /home


Step 4: Set selinux to permissive mode in /etc/selinux/config file

Step 5: Package Installation
sudo yum groupinstall XFCE

restart

Step 6: Restoring Configuration Files:
ssh_config hosts hosts.allow hosts.deny cups.config 


Step 7: Packages Installation
vim-x11 qcad subversion gv yumex texlive xdvik openoffice aspell alpine gimp tkdiff vncserver java unrar paw x11vnc logwatch tgif texlive-latex

Step 8: Setting RPMs
atrpm, adoberpm

Step 9: Install adobe & adobe-flashplayer

Step 10: Auto-start sshd
hkconfig --level 2345 sshd on
service sshd restart

